msgstr "collapseTree"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/browser.rst:50
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Settings --> Interface Customization` it is possible to "
"disable resources. If you, for instance, would not like to show Python "
"scripts in the browser, you can uncheck the :menuselection:`Browser --> py` "
"entry, and if you want to get rid of your home folder in the browser, you "
"can uncheck the :menuselection:`Browser --> special:Home` entry."
msgstr ""
"I :menuselection:`Inställningar --> Interface Customization` är det möjligt "
"att inaktivera resurser. Om du t.ex. inte vill visa Python-skript i "
"bläddraren kan du avmarkera posten :menuselection:`Bläddrare --> py`, och om"
" du vill bli av med din hemmapp i webbläsaren kan du avmarkera posten "
":menuselection:`Bläddrare --> special:Home`."

